name: Agog 15 Wonton Orbs
description: @__lindaloh__ 3D sculpture of amorphous form, vaguely spherical, but with nurb tails. It is coloured from a video art texture of multiple orbs. One of a collection of 20 individual sculptural pieces from my VR world "Agog", 2021. They are variously luminous, poetic, evocative, shiny, scribbly, wacky, simple, sleek, golden, wonky, clashing, compelling, weird, colourful, minimal, maximal, simple, ethereal...
